<p>72. Rwanda commended the progress made by Andorra in promoting and protecting 
</p>
<p>human rights since its first universal periodic review. It noted with appreciation that 
</p>
<p>Andorra has ratified 15 instruments, including the optional protocols and the 
</p>
<p>additional protocols to conventions to which it was already a party. Rwanda 
</p>
<p>commended the adoption of the Act on the Elimination of Gender -based and Domestic 
</p>
<p>Violence and the establishment of the National Commission on the same subject.  
</p>
<p>73. Sierra Leone praised the commitment of Andorra to human rights, especially its 
</p>
<p>advancement on children&#8217;s rights and the prohibition of corporal punishment. 
</p>
