</b></p>
<p>84.48 Ensure that further steps are taken to address anti<b>-</b>discrimination issues 
</p>
<p>and ensure that the National Plan of Action for Equality addresses all areas of the 
</p>
<p>Convention on the Elimination of All Forms of Discrimination against Women 
</p>
