</b></p>
<p>84.64 Review its legislation so that it provides legal support for collective 
</p>
<p>bargaining and the right to strike (Sweden); <b> 
</b></p>
<p>84.65 Pursue its efforts in eradicating unemployment, in particular through the 
</p>
